{"tid":1874531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港上班　東莞睡　天天過關常平姑爺樂於奔波","createTime":"2020-02-11T09:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T09:15:49.000Z","uid":297241,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"09a2ce09e25887764f46c89947cca72a520d8730","tid":1874531,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:04:14.000Z","msg":"港上班　東莞睡　天天過關<br />\n常平姑爺樂於奔波<br />\n<br />\n每天傍晚，羅湖橋頭都有數以萬計的中港姑爺拖着疲憊身軀排隊過關，趕回內地與家人團聚。現年四十三歲的鍾炳祥是人群中的一個，他每天往返東莞常平與香港之間已五年，「香港搵唔到老婆咪返大陸娶，吃得鹹魚抵得渴，但估唔到咁辛苦！」若一切可以從頭再來，這位人稱祥哥的常平姑爺說，他仍會這樣做，因為愛是無悔。<br />\n<br />\n任印刷機械維修的祥哥，六年前被公司派上東莞常平公幹，<span style=\"color: red;\">在廠中認識了一位較他年輕十五歲的河南姑娘，兩人一見鍾情，隨即結合</span>，他從此開始了中港兩邊頻撲的常平姑爺生涯。"},{"pid":"f6d691112813115b18042aba91f7420591a8cea9","tid":1874531,"uid":102078,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:07:51.000Z","msg":"以前返得東莞常平都係叫雞多"},{"pid":"ab85b838d43f43f26b5d83d6231c744340ecbf83","tid":1874531,"uid":161151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知邊間場識呢？"},{"pid":"0093e947230b0c6d304cca585be2a736367cf15f","tid":1874531,"uid":74751,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:10:58.000Z","msg":"係呀係呀 唔撚比鄉下係東莞既？"},{"pid":"77d4175e451c002d6594870d378986587b886b3a","tid":1874531,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:13:35.000Z","msg":"呢單20年都嚟緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b01f078208b345b00875f426c75f55b9a0a58d5d","tid":1874531,"uid":124439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:13:53.000Z","msg":"愛是無悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa923f74c2ee59d04f3398334f8c211f198439f","tid":1874531,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"09a2ce09e25887764f46c89947cca